Is YOUR makeup still not giving what you want it to sis?

I think our days of just relying on YouTube isn’t enough anymore. 

You can watch and save all the YouTube videos you want but if you don’t understand why you are doing certain things then it won’t make sense at all. 

So here’s what you do: 
1️⃣ Find a makeup artist whose work resonates with your style of makeup 
2️⃣ Book a makeup class with a knowledgeable makeup artist. (May require some travel) 
3️⃣ Ask as many questions as you need to
4️⃣Book your makeup class 
5️⃣ Take plenty of notes during your class 
6️⃣ Practice Practice Practice

Now, you can sit back with a peace of mind when you do your makeup the next time. 

Let me know in the comments if you found this helpful!

RED FLAGS 🚩 🚩🚩
